  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.58,
      "text": "굿모닝 팝스 홈페이지 성취자 게시판에 남겨주세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 2.58,
      "end": 18.74,
      "text": "1일 아침 6시 조정현의 굿모닝 팝스 해봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 20.58,
      "end": 25.74,
      "text": "조정현의 굿모닝 팝스"
    },
    {
      "start": 25.74,
      "end": 29.22,
      "text": "조정현의 굿모닝 팝스"
    },
    {
      "start": 29.22,
      "end": 42.46,
      "text": "English"
    },
    {
      "start": 42.46,
      "end": 63.12,
      "text": "다막 없이 영화를 볼 수 있는 그날까지"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.12,
      "end": 64.68,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.68,
      "end": 66.92,
      "text": "11월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.92,
      "end": 70.22,
      "text": "사랑과 인생에 관한 통찰을 느끼게 해주는"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.22,
      "end": 72.48,
      "text": "The Seagull Karmegi"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.48,
      "end": 73.54,
      "text": "어서오세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 73.64,
      "end": 74.14,
      "text": "Good day"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.14,
      "end": 76.92,
      "text": "Hello, Joe Sam. Hello, GM Peers. Good morning."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.34,
      "end": 77.74,
      "text": "Good morning. Good morning."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.74,
      "end": 78.08,
      "text": "Good morning."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.08,
      "end": 81.9,
      "text": "아, 이 영화에서 정말 아름답다."
    },
    {
      "start": 82.04,
      "end": 85.68,
      "text": "참 예쁘다라고 생각했던 배우가 한 명이 있었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.76,
      "end": 87.9,
      "text": "I think I know who you're referring to."
    },
    {
      "start": 88.04,
      "end": 90.52,
      "text": "그렇죠. 니나 역할의 배우였는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 90.52,
      "end": 93.86,
      "text": "원래 이름이 굉장히 어렵더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.86,
      "end": 95.48,
      "text": "철자를 보면 왠지"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.48,
      "end": 98.62,
      "text": "S-S-E-R-C-E-R-O-N-N-N"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.62,
      "end": 101.4,
      "text": "이런 식으로 발음을 해야 될 것 같은 생각이 들었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 101.86,
      "end": 102.52,
      "text": "역대급"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.52,
      "end": 105.36,
      "text": "S-A-O-I-R-S-E"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.36,
      "end": 108.8,
      "text": "So she is well-known as an actress"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.8,
      "end": 110.78,
      "text": "and she goes on many TV shows"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.78,
      "end": 113.58,
      "text": "and is interviewed on American television"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.58,
      "end": 117.5,
      "text": "and every time the host asks the same question."
    },
    {
      "start": 117.58,
      "end": 119.6,
      "text": "How to pronounce her name?"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.62,
      "end": 119.96,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.98,
      "end": 120.4,
      "text": "Exactly."
    },
    {
      "start": 120.74,
      "end": 122.2,
      "text": "Nobody knows how to pronounce this."
    },
    {
      "start": 122.2,
      "end": 123.88,
      "text": "How can we pronounce your name?"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.9,
      "end": 124.78,
      "text": "Even native speakers?"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.24,
      "end": 126.48,
      "text": "Well, this is not a native,"
    },
    {
      "start": 126.86,
      "end": 128.46,
      "text": "it doesn't sound like an American name"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.46,
      "end": 130.46,
      "text": "and it doesn't,"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.7,
      "end": 133.82,
      "text": "the pronunciation is not like the spelling at all."
    },
    {
      "start": 133.82,
      "end": 134.82,
      "text": "어떻게 해요 그러면?"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.9,
      "end": 135.46,
      "text": "혹시 아세요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 135.46,
      "end": 137.08,
      "text": "Let me see."
    },
    {
      "start": 137.24,
      "end": 137.38,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 137.5,
      "end": 138.6,
      "text": "If I remember correctly"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.6,
      "end": 140.38,
      "text": "Sure-She?"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.72,
      "end": 141.16,
      "text": "Sersha?"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.64,
      "end": 142.08,
      "text": "Sersha?"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.2,
      "end": 142.66,
      "text": "Sersha?"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.84,
      "end": 143.02,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.24,
      "end": 143.96,
      "text": "I think it's Sersha."
    },
    {
      "start": 144.24,
      "end": 144.5,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 144.64,
      "end": 146.18,
      "text": "Actually, I watched one video."
    },
    {
      "start": 147.02,
      "end": 147.78,
      "text": "And you remember?"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.92,
      "end": 148.2,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 148.26,
      "end": 151.3,
      "text": "Where she explained how to pronounce her name precisely."
    },
    {
      "start": 151.5,
      "end": 153.4,
      "text": "She must be sick of getting that question"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.4,
      "end": 154.1,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 154.12,
      "end": 154.84,
      "text": "Every interview."
    },
    {
      "start": 154.94,
      "end": 158.36,
      "text": "어떤 다른 사람이 스시 이렇게 발음도 하더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 158.54,
      "end": 159.42,
      "text": "약간 조크처럼."
    },
    {
      "start": 159.74,
      "end": 159.96,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 160.16,
      "end": 161.04,
      "text": "근데 서샤."
    },
    {
      "start": 161.32,
      "end": 162.12,
      "text": "세올시야?"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.48,
      "end": 163.12,
      "text": "서샤."
    },
    {
      "start": 163.26,
      "end": 166.26,
      "text": "Yeah, 서샤 이렇게 발음을 한다고 알려주더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 166.5,
      "end": 169.54,
      "text": "She's an American-born Irish actress."
    },
    {
      "start": 169.92,
      "end": 174.9,
      "text": "She said she's an Irish, but the spelling of her name is too Irish to pronounce."
    },
    {
      "start": 175.16,
      "end": 176.1,
      "text": "Too Irish."
    },
    {
      "start": 176.16,
      "end": 177.14,
      "text": "그게 문제라고 했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 177.3,
      "end": 178.72,
      "text": "너무 Irish이라서 탈이야."
    },
    {
      "start": 178.72,
      "end": 179.04,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 179.24,
      "end": 181.56,
      "text": "Even Irish people can't pronounce it."
    },
    {
      "start": 181.56,
      "end": 187.3,
      "text": "Okay, so it's not just us Americans, even her own people, her own country people."
    },
    {
      "start": 187.62,
      "end": 193.92,
      "text": "그래서 우리가 만약에 인터넷에 검색을 하면 뭐 시얼샤, 로넌 이렇게 적혀있는 것을 볼 수가 있는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.92,
      "end": 200.54,
      "text": "정확한 발음은 이제 서샤, 아니면 서샤 이렇게 비슷하게 발음을 하시면 될 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 200.76,
      "end": 203.24,
      "text": "Yeah, please excuse us if we're a little off."
    },
    {
      "start": 203.74,
      "end": 204.46,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 204.58,
      "end": 206.48,
      "text": "원어민한테도 어려운 발음은 당연합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 206.48,
      "end": 208.94,
      "text": "And she's in her late 20s."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.1,
      "end": 210.2,
      "text": "She's very young."
    },
    {
      "start": 210.2,
      "end": 213.72,
      "text": "Oh, born in 1994 and has won various awards."
    },
    {
      "start": 214.1,
      "end": 217.42,
      "text": "Yeah, she's won many awards and been nominated for many awards."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.82,
      "end": 225.1,
      "text": "She's actually the second youngest actress to receive three Oscar nominations before the age of 24."
    },
    {
      "start": 225.2,
      "end": 225.66,
      "text": "Wonderful."
    },
    {
      "start": 226.18,
      "end": 229.94,
      "text": "The first one was Jennifer Lawrence and she is the second in history."
    },
    {
      "start": 229.94,
      "end": 235.02,
      "text": "So she has received many, many awards and nominations before 30."
    },
    {
      "start": 235.16,
      "end": 236.72,
      "text": "Wow, 진짜 멋지네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 236.72,
      "end": 237.16,
      "text": "At a young age."
    },
    {
      "start": 237.26,
      "end": 237.98,
      "text": "몰랐어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.34,
      "end": 240.42,
      "text": "멋지네요, 진짜."
    },
    {
      "start": 240.9,
      "end": 247.02,
      "text": "Yeah, she was nominated for her third Oscar for a movie called Lady Bird in 2017."
    },
    {
      "start": 248.06,
      "end": 252.78,
      "text": "And you probably haven't seen it, but she was nominated for many awards."
    },
    {
      "start": 252.78,
      "end": 253.2,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 253.4,
      "end": 255.92,
      "text": "And she's a much beloved actress."
    },
    {
      "start": 256.3,
      "end": 259.92,
      "text": "And she's a much beloved actress."
    },
    {
      "start": 260.34,
      "end": 261.0,
      "text": "Little woman."
    },
    {
      "start": 261.12,
      "end": 261.46,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 262.0,
      "end": 262.94,
      "text": "Based on the book."
    },
    {
      "start": 263.08,
      "end": 263.34,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 263.74,
      "end": 267.08,
      "text": "작은아씨들이라는 소설 읽어보신 분들 많이 계실 텐데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.68,
      "end": 270.78,
      "text": "그래서 최근에 이 영화가 또 나왔습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 270.78,
      "end": 272.66,
      "text": "네, 거기에서 she played Joe."
    },
    {
      "start": 273.1,
      "end": 275.42,
      "text": "Ah, Joe, like a girl's name, Joe."
    },
    {
      "start": 275.52,
      "end": 280.66,
      "text": "Yeah, 둘째, 자매 중에서 둘째의 역할, Joe의 역할을 맡았더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 280.84,
      "end": 281.68,
      "text": "작은아씨들에서."
    },
    {
      "start": 281.96,
      "end": 284.96,
      "text": "And the movie that I saw was The Grand Budapest Hotel."
    },
    {
      "start": 285.14,
      "end": 286.24,
      "text": "She was in that."
    },
    {
      "start": 286.38,
      "end": 288.1,
      "text": "My wife and I really enjoyed that movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 288.22,
      "end": 289.9,
      "text": "네, 이 영화도 아주 유명한데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.12,
      "end": 296.14,
      "text": "아무튼 이렇게 중요한 영화, 굵은 영화에서 아주 역할을 잘 맡은 배우인 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 296.34,
      "end": 297.74,
      "text": "Yeah, she's a good actress."
    },
    {
      "start": 297.74,
      "end": 299.82,
      "text": "네, 오늘 장면 먼저 듣고 오겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 299.82,
      "end": 301.54,
      "text": "Why are you so nervous?"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.92,
      "end": 302.36,
      "text": "I'm not."
    },
    {
      "start": 303.16,
      "end": 306.22,
      "text": "Well, I'm not afraid to perform for your mother, but"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.22,
      "end": 308.78,
      "text": "Boris Tregorin, he's so famous."
    },
    {
      "start": 309.06,
      "end": 310.98,
      "text": "I'm embarrassed to act in front of him."
    },
    {
      "start": 311.78,
      "end": 312.48,
      "text": "He looked young."
    },
    {
      "start": 313.02,
      "end": 314.68,
      "text": "He is young and accomplished."
    },
    {
      "start": 314.8,
      "end": 315.42,
      "text": "Don't remind me."
    },
    {
      "start": 316.1,
      "end": 317.46,
      "text": "His stories are incredible."
    },
    {
      "start": 318.52,
      "end": 320.76,
      "text": "Well, his stories are full of life."
    },
    {
      "start": 321.38,
      "end": 322.84,
      "text": "In your plays, everyone's dead."
    },
    {
      "start": 324.3,
      "end": 325.02,
      "text": "Uh-oh, drama."
    },
    {
      "start": 325.02,
      "end": 326.82,
      "text": "I sense some drama."
    },
    {
      "start": 327.1,
      "end": 328.02,
      "text": "Some jealousy."
    },
    {
      "start": 328.72,
      "end": 329.28,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 329.28,
      "end": 332.0,
      "text": "그런데 어저께, 컨스탄틴이 마지막에,"
    },
    {
      "start": 332.14,
      "end": 335.08,
      "text": "Even the thought of her makes my heart race."
    },
    {
      "start": 335.2,
      "end": 336.62,
      "text": "I'm insanely happy."
    },
    {
      "start": 336.82,
      "end": 337.78,
      "text": "I love her."
    },
    {
      "start": 337.94,
      "end": 338.96,
      "text": "딱 그 말을 했는데."
    },
    {
      "start": 339.34,
      "end": 339.74,
      "text": "Oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 340.58,
      "end": 342.86,
      "text": "그리고, obviously, Nina가 seemed to love him."
    },
    {
      "start": 343.66,
      "end": 348.08,
      "text": "첫 장면에서는 둘 다 되게 사랑을 하는 느낌이 분명히 들었었는데."
    },
    {
      "start": 348.18,
      "end": 349.44,
      "text": "They looked like they got along."
    },
    {
      "start": 349.58,
      "end": 349.84,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 349.84,
      "end": 352.56,
      "text": "But she cared too much for another one, Boris."
    },
    {
      "start": 353.02,
      "end": 354.2,
      "text": "This other guy."
    },
    {
      "start": 354.2,
      "end": 354.58,
      "text": "That's right."
    },
    {
      "start": 354.58,
      "end": 356.38,
      "text": "This other gnome came in."
    },
    {
      "start": 356.42,
      "end": 356.82,
      "text": "That's right."
    },
    {
      "start": 356.82,
      "end": 359.82,
      "text": "And he happens to be a famous author."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.06,
      "end": 360.3,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.84,
      "end": 362.44,
      "text": "컨스탄틴의 어머니 있잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 362.74,
      "end": 365.02,
      "text": "이리나가 데려온 애인이 있는데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 365.52,
      "end": 372.16,
      "text": "그 보리스에 대해서 지금 니나가 굉장히 호감을 보이고 있는 상황이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 372.16,
      "end": 373.52,
      "text": "He's so famous."
    },
    {
      "start": 373.76,
      "end": 374.52,
      "text": "He's so popular."
    },
    {
      "start": 375.12,
      "end": 376.38,
      "text": "Imagine Constantine."
    },
    {
      "start": 376.72,
      "end": 377.38,
      "text": "His 심정."
    },
    {
      "start": 377.56,
      "end": 378.78,
      "text": "How he feels right now."
    },
    {
      "start": 378.88,
      "end": 381.28,
      "text": "굉장히 jealous of him 했을 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 382.08,
      "end": 383.88,
      "text": "표현들 먼저 점검을 해보겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 384.72,
      "end": 385.64,
      "text": "I'm embarrassed."
    },
    {
      "start": 386.02,
      "end": 387.06,
      "text": "I'm embarrassed."
    },
    {
      "start": 387.5,
      "end": 388.38,
      "text": "쑥스러워."
    },
    {
      "start": 388.7,
      "end": 389.42,
      "text": "창피해."
    },
    {
      "start": 389.68,
      "end": 390.38,
      "text": "I'm embarrassed."
    },
    {
      "start": 391.74,
      "end": 393.6,
      "text": "Young and accomplished."
    },
    {
      "start": 394.16,
      "end": 395.98,
      "text": "젊고, accomplished."
    },
    {
      "start": 396.48,
      "end": 397.04,
      "text": "성공한."
    },
    {
      "start": 397.04,
      "end": 398.68,
      "text": "Oh, she's talking about him."
    },
    {
      "start": 398.78,
      "end": 399.48,
      "text": "Yeah, Boris."
    },
    {
      "start": 399.58,
